{"tid":1010620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"魔熊仔出沒？小男孩森林失蹤3天　奇蹟獲救語出驚人：熊熊陪我玩","createTime":"2019-02-06T06:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T07:17:40.000Z","uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3383a83c58f577c43beebfee85bfe372049e1ec4","tid":1010620,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3884/d3884064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3884%2Fd3884064.jpg&h=fdf6d722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小男孩在森林裡離奇消失3天，獲救後堅稱自己是被熊救了。（圖／翻攝自Facebook／The Dodo）<br />\n寵物小組／綜合報導<br />\n沒人知道在森林裡發生了什麼事，但可以肯定的是，最後的結局非常可愛。3歲的小男孩凱西（Casey Hathaway）和家人一起住在美國北卡羅萊納州的克雷文小鎮，但就在幾天前，他和其他小朋友一起在院子裡玩耍，接下來卻令所有人擔心死了。（ETtoday寵物雲有IG了，快按追蹤）<br />\n到了吃飯時間，凱西的曾祖母到處都找不到曾孫，過了幾個小時，才終於打電話給警察，眾人進到森林裡搜索，幾個小時過去、一天、兩天過去還是找不到人，警犬在灌木叢裡到處嗅聞，同時間氣溫不斷下降，所有人都擔心死了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3884/d3884065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3884%2Fd3884065.jpg&h=315cd7bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲辛苦搜索的警長，抱著幸運獲救的小男孩，他相信熊的故事是真的。<br />\n情況如此嚴峻，連搜索的警長都說，如果凱西過了這麼久還活著，那將會是了不起的奇蹟。但就在這時，奇蹟真的發生了！搜索隊中一名男子聽到小聲呼叫，隨著深入樹林，經過一個冰凍住的池塘，這才發現小凱西就躲在一個石洞裡。<br />\n凱西被發現時體溫很低，手指和身上有凍傷，但還活著！他在醫院裡告訴媽媽一個神奇的故事，他說他迷路了，有一隻熊照顧著他，「我和一隻熊待在一起兩天，牠是上帝派來幫助我的好人。」<br />\n這段奇聞立刻成了全球網友熱烈討論的話題，許多人覺得不可能，但負責搜索的警長這樣說「這是一個非常可愛的故事，如果這是那個孩子之所以能度過難關的原因，你知道嗎？我相信。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3884/d3884066.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3884%2Fd3884066.jpg&h=bfd3d05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小男孩獲救堅持自己和熊在一起玩了兩天。（圖／取自免費圖庫unsplash）<br />\n<a href=\"https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1373524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpets.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1373524&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=d2bf7141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1373524</a>"},{"pid":"7c5ec701620b697cd70716ccd9d50e313e7b0a9e","tid":1010620,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"Jungle Book<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89efe3173f34b8885322d3ef705c941b19d7fae5","tid":1010620,"uid":234695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:25:41.000Z","msg":"D文筆好似揭尾故，尤其係最尾個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c704d0758e9a8bebc41c8dcc1656c5d0451b7ac","tid":1010620,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:53:52.000Z","msg":"然後擊殺咗隻熊未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929c60dbde419e62211f75965f371c41220f56fd","tid":1010620,"uid":61954,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.biaoqing.com/work/20170625/125605013.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.biaoqing.com%2Fwork%2F20170625%2F125605013.gif&h=1a4e8edd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f25ea52bdd8d20a29719c7d7a301f5348a109e14","tid":1010620,"uid":164730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"好正常，熊都有好人"},{"pid":"76109bfb53a80d59c9efed6295784c0df5726f90","tid":1010620,"uid":37502,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i0.sinaimg.cn/ent/z/v/2014-08-02/U11177P28T3D4185181F326DT20140802121306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fz%2Fv%2F2014-08-02%2FU11177P28T3D4185181F326DT20140802121306.jpg&h=c0d6b7a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f185145c177446de7509df60547c53fabfac1e61","tid":1010620,"uid":72647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"隻熊養住佢，過兩日凍d 先食"},{"pid":"5c7557cc74a6cd77fdcef94f0682b13e7a1fb82